===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|lous}}, {{m|enm|lows}}, {{m|enm|lowse}}, from {{inh|en|ang|lūs}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*lūs}} (compare West Frisian {{m|fy|lûs}}, Dutch {{m|nl|luis}}, German Low German {{m|nds-de|Luus}}, German {{m|de|Laus}}, from {{der|en|ine-pro|*lewH-}} (compare Welsh {{m|cy|llau||lice}}, Tocharian B {{m|txb|luwo}}, maybe Sanskrit {{m|sa|यूका}}).

